4. Corrections were made in real-time (causal bias, refresh rate assumptions)
5. Once corrected, the recognitions held stable within the conversation window
6. The conversation became evidence to be folded into the framework

The framework doesn't just describe transmission—it enables it by being structured as a resonant cavity that shapes what enters it toward coherence with its pattern.

